\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1 tablespoon black peppercorns\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 tablespoon whole white peppercorns\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons whole {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/coriander/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 coriander}} seeds\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 tablespoon red pepper flakes\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons dark brown sugar, loosely packed\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons kosher salt\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/skirt-steak/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 skirt steak}}, about 2 pounds, cut into 4 pieces\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 tablespoons {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/canola-oil/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 canola oil}}, divided\
